<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="About Khushi - Full-Stack Developer passionate about innovative web solutions">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Khushi, about, full-stack developer, web development, skills, education">
    <meta name="author" content="Khushi">
    <title>About - Khushi's Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.ico">
    <!-- Google Fonts: Poppins + Playfair Display -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-300 to-teal-400">
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    <!-- About Me Section -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <!-- Photo and Bio -->
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 mb-16">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 fade-in delay-50">
                    <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Khushi's Profile Photo" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
                    <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-playfair mb-6 text-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 hover:text-gray-700 fade-in delay-100">About Me</h2>
                    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins leading-relaxed text-gray-900 mb-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:text-gray-700 fade-in delay-150">
                        Hi! I'm Khushi, a passionate Full-Stack Developer currently interning as a Teaching Assistant at Apna college community, where I solve MERN-related queries and assist peers. I thrive on building innovative web solutions and have a strong foundation in MERN stack, DSA with Java, MySQL, and MongoDB. My journey in tech is fueled by curiosity and a love for problem-solving.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Education, Skills, and Achievements -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg fade-in delay-200">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-playfair mb-4 text-gray-900">Education</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg font-poppins text-gray-900">B.Tech in Computer Engineering<br>Shri Ram Institute of Technology, Jabalpur<br>CGPA: 7.8</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg fade-in delay-250">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-playfair mb-4 text-gray-900">Skills</h3>
                    <ul class="text-lg font-poppins text-gray-900 list-disc list-inside">
                        <li>MERN Stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js)</li>
                        <li>DSA with Java</li>
                        <li>MySQL, MongoDB</li>
                        <li>Web Development</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg fade-in delay-300">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-playfair mb-4 text-gray-900">Achievements</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg font-poppins text-gray-900">
                        Participated in a hackathon at IIT Roorkee’s Tech Fest, earning recognition for innovative ideas. Earned certifications from Sigma 4.0 in MERN Development, Web Development, and DSA.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Journey -->
            <div class="mt-20">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-playfair mb-8 text-center text-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 hover:text-gray-700 fade-in delay-350">My Journey</h3>
                <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg fade-in delay-400">
                    <p class="text-xl font-poppins leading-relaxed text-center text-gray-900 transition-all duration-300 hover:text-gray-700">
                        My tech journey began with a passion for coding, leading me to pursue B.Tech at Shri Ram Institute of Technology. I’ve honed my skills in MERN and DSA, participating in a hackathon at IIT Roorkee’s Tech Fest, where my team showcased innovative ideas. I also earned certifications like Sigma 4.0 in MERN and Development, and DSA, reflecting my dedication to growth.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            setTimeout(() => {
                document.body.classList.add('loaded');
            }, 100); // Slight delay to ensure page renders
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>